title: Hints - Converse Rubber Tracks: Track of the Week
description:
The single "All At Once" by Hints is this week's "Track of the Week". The four-piece were aware from the start of their time in the studio and worked to make the most of every moment at Converse Rubber Tracks. Watch the band record their original single "All At Once," evaluate the recorded track amongst themselves and the studio engineer, and work to complete the final version at Converse Rubber Tracks. 
For more on Converse Rubber Tracks, check out:
www.converse.com/rubbertracks
